body:
This PR implements the orographic drag following [Garner05](https://journals.ametsoc.org/view/journals/atsc/62/7/jas3496.1.xml?tab_body=pdf).

- [x] Obtain topo info and regrid to model grid;
- [x] Implement drag computation;
- [ ] ~Tests~ (leave the physical tests to a separate PR);
- [x] [Documentation](https://www.overleaf.com/read/qhnsjtthnyvf);
- [x] Code restructure with recent main updates.
